Title: 'When Pinays meets Latinos '
DateModified: '2019-02-19'
DatePublished: '2019-02-19'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/when-pinays-meets-latinos
SetInCountry: Philippines
Category: Making a local connection
AuthorName: Grace Abonal
AuthorCountry: United Arab Emirates
Text: When I was a child, my eldest brother who works as a seaman always tells me
  stories about Portugal. People are religious and hospitable. He said their characters
  are almost the same as Filipinos. So I grew up, become fascinated about them..
